{"tid":1725813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講解如何應對二噁英 （由中大化學博士，前中大講師講解）","createTime":"2019-11-16T01:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T07:24:29.000Z","uid":172129,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f37c9315872a517593def837c8fdac3c79d68ee5","tid":1725813,"uid":172129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:27:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/179179469403545/posts/453229281998561?vh=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F179179469403545%2Fposts%2F453229281998561%3Fvh%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BEPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=6e22d859\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/179179469403545/posts/453229281998561?vh=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n文字版重點<br />\n<br />\n一 ： 即使豬嘴都係唔足夠應對二噁英，以外國例子，清理二噁英係會穿生化裝備<br />\n<br />\n二： 受污染既地區的泥土其實係要全鏟走，但香港環境係唔可能<br />\n<br />\n三 ：如果處於受污染環境，儘量包裹全身<br />\n<br />\n四 ：逗留過污染地區既既手足/記者最好將穿過的衣服銷毀，呢個係簡單做法， 「衣服清洗乾淨」呢個方法唔建議，相對複雜<br />\n<br />\n五： 在之前有中大手足在運動場地面睡覺，呢個係好有問題，應該要避免皮膚接觸災區<br />\n<br />\n六： 有一點好肯定就係，從有前線警既子女都有對催淚彈敏感情況，顯示出即使未去過災區，只要將污染物帶回居住地方都會受影響"},{"pid":"480c17cf4cca0877962b7b1dbdd8be054fe073ae","tid":1725813,"uid":172129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:27:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f689fd4ff559aef1c3bf6a5d370720889fcd3c68","tid":1725813,"uid":172129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:27:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ecb9cdf22dc4b7ea97497280a040901bc5d66cb3","tid":1725813,"uid":172129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:27:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a135d00865f9c7ae7a75d9b9725693b0a2996e24","tid":1725813,"uid":172129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:27:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6998b89c8fa9b9ecc43d689694d4cbf1448e9d9a","tid":1725813,"uid":172129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:28:05.000Z","msg":"推